# 🌟 Features of Spring Framework

## 1. Lightweight

Spring is lightweight because it uses Plain Old Java Objects (POJOs).

---

## 2. Dependency Injection (DI)

Objects do not create their own dependencies.

Instead, Spring provides them automatically.

---

## 3. Inversion of Control (IoC)

Spring manages the lifecycle and creation of objects.

---

## 4. Aspect-Oriented Programming (AOP)

Separates cross-cutting concerns like:

* Logging
* Security
* Transaction Management

---

## 5. Modular Design

Spring consists of independent modules that can be used separately.

